    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先初始化gitGraph，方向设为TB自上而下。创建第一个commit，然后从main切出develop分支，切换到develop做第一次提交。",
      "elements_involved": [
